title: ArtBin 6892AG 2-Tray Art Supply Box, Portable Art & Craft Organizer with Lift-Up Trays, [1] Plastic Storage Case, Gray/Black
description: Perfect for the crafter on the go! ArtBin Tray Boxes feature a tight, secure latch and carrying handle so that you can easily take your supplies with you wherever you go.The quick access lift-out tray storage can be used to store smaller items, while the large open area in the bottom of the box allows for storage of bulkier supplies such as paint bottles, large stamp pads, scissors, glues, vinyl rolls and more.
